## Installation

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.8+
- pip or conda

### Quick Install
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### Development Install
```bash
git clone https://github.com/user/repo.git
cd repo
pip install -e .
```

---

## Quick Start

```python
from project import Model

# Load model
model = Model()

# Train
model.fit(X_train, y_train)

# Predict
predictions = model.predict(X_test)
```

